WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:02.379
Previously on AMC's "The Son"...

00:02.382 --> 00:03.484
Daddy?

00:03.487 --> 00:05.942
You have no idea what
you did to this family.

00:05.945 --> 00:08.454
My daddy's gonna pay for
what he did. I promise you.

00:08.456 --> 00:10.256
Prodigal son has returned.

00:10.258 --> 00:11.601
You weren't here!

00:11.604 --> 00:13.468
Eli! Apaches.

00:13.471 --> 00:15.130
- They must have known the warriors were gone.
- Yeah.

00:15.132 --> 00:17.663
He's drilling slantways to hook my oil.

00:17.665 --> 00:19.532
This act of thievery ends tonight.

00:19.534 --> 00:21.301
- Come on, boys, faster.
- More.

00:21.303 --> 00:22.835
Someone's coming!

00:22.837 --> 00:24.837
- Ulysses, right?
- Yes, ma'am.

00:24.839 --> 00:26.703
You only got one chance.

00:26.706 --> 00:27.726
Get!

