05:05.313 --> 05:06.960
- Maria?
- A moment, mister.

05:06.963 --> 05:08.378
_

05:08.381 --> 05:10.335
Where you going? Hey, Maria.

05:10.345 --> 05:11.967
_

05:12.289 --> 05:14.265
_

05:14.268 --> 05:15.735
Maria!

05:15.738 --> 05:18.005
Maria, tell them we're together! Maria!

05:18.008 --> 05:19.273
Come back!

05:23.282 --> 05:26.250
Maria!

05:26.253 --> 05:28.186
Maria, come back!

05:28.189 --> 05:29.823
Come back!

05:29.826 --> 05:32.000
We're together! Maria!

